asically an initial prompt + persona + personal agent knowledge\n2) Option to connect existing machine as a connector to the Agent, to run actions on the user's machine when authorized, e.g., Claude Cowork, Claude Dispatch\n3) \"Brain\" concept from the Pewdipie's Odysseus agent\n4) Integration with email and calendar, to not only give a model access to users calendar events and mail, but display it in the interface, to be make an agent all-in-one toolkit\n5) n8n-like (or integration with it) to allow for workflows in the app, that can be both triggered by the assistant, by the user or by an automation (e.g., process mails, messages, etc.) with integration with the systems in the app, like knowledge base, tools, assistants, brains, memory, agents and so on",
